# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# The app runs with or without an API key — missing key degrades generate gracefully.

# Anthropic API key — used by generate.ts to call Claude.
# If absent: generate returns retrieved context instead of an LLM response.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Ollama URL — LIVE as of lesson 103. OllamaEmbedder calls it to embed corpus
# chunks and queries (nomic-embed-text, 768-dim). Defaults to the value below if
# unset, so you only need to set this to point at a non-default host/port.
# Unlike ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, this is a HARD dependency at ingest/query time —
# embedding cannot degrade gracefully (no vectors = nothing to search).
OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434
